Title:
Public Disclaimer — Important Information for All Creators

Body:
The IP Continuity Watermark Standard, the Repost Badge, and the VaultForge‑Live continuity system are not legal services and do not replace copyright law, legal advice, or formal legal protection.

These tools provide visibility, timestamping, and continuity, but they do not:

act as legal filings

register your copyright

guarantee legal outcomes

prevent copying

provide financial protection

replace professional legal counsel

Creators should not rely on this system as their only method of protection, especially in situations involving commercial use, licensing, disputes, or financial risk.

This system is designed to support creators, not to serve as a legal shield.
For legal questions, consult a qualified professional.

Use this system for visibility and continuity — not as a substitute for legal protection.
